newest.message:
== Contributors for this version ==
* Jimi
== Bug Fixes ==
* Fixed a crash bug in Attribute Optimizer when selecting optimization of a characters entire trained skills. * Corrected Thukker Component Assembly Array facility material bonus.
== Enhancements ==
* Added position number in skill queue list. * Added clone jump and neural availability indicators. * Added jump clones implants info of a character in Implant Groups tool.
== Misc ==
* Excluded history orders from being uploaded to EMDR from EMUU after request from EMDR owner. * EMUU will no longer upload data if there is no data to upload. * Removed Clone Grade/SP/Notification. * Several improvements have been done to the base code to make EVEMon a better application.
